This is a blog application. 
On you terminal, cd to the directory of this application and type following commands one by one:
	source myvenv/bin/activate
	python manage.py runserver
This will run the server on your computer
Now type the URL http://localhost:8000/ on your browser to see the blog!!!

A non-authenticated user can see posts and add comments to the posts.
An authenticated user can see, add, edit and delete posts. He can also approve the comments added by a non-authenticated user so that they can be displayed on the blog.
